parsedComplaintsResult.issueCategory: Engine Failure due to Oil Sludge
parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the engine can cause the vehicle to stall or lose power, leading to accidents or leaving the driver stranded.
symptoms: The engine oil light comes on
the engine makes a knocking or grinding noise
the vehicle stalls or loses power
white smoke comes out of the exhaust
oil leaks from the engine
and the engine overheats.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the cooling system can cause the engine to overheat, leading to engine damage or failure.
symptoms: The temperature gauge rises
coolant leaks from the radiator or hoses
the engine overheats
and white smoke comes out of the exhaust.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the transmission can cause the vehicle to lose power or stall, leading to accidents or leaving the driver stranded.
symptoms: The transmission slips or hesitates
the vehicle loses power or stalls
and the transmission warning light comes on.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the transmission can cause the vehicle to stall, lose power, or become stuck in gear, leading to accidents or leaving the driver stranded.
symptoms: The transmission slips or hesitates
the engine light comes on
the transmission drops into a lower gear
the vehicle stalls or loses power
the transmission makes a loud noise
the RPMs rev high
and the vehicle is unable to shift into gear.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the clutch master cylinder can cause the clutch pedal to stick to the floor, making it difficult or impossible to shift gears, which can lead to accidents or leave the driver stranded.
symptoms: The clutch pedal feels soft or spongy
the clutch pedal sticks to the floor
the clutch pedal does not return to its normal position
the clutch pedal has a delayed return to its normal position
the clutch pedal has a sudden loss of pressure.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The oil leak can cause the engine to fail, leading to accidents or leaving the driver stranded.
symptoms: Oil leak from the engine block
smoke coming from under the hood
engine failure
check engine light comes on.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the transmission speed sensor can cause the transmission to malfunction, leading to accidents or leaving the driver stranded.
symptoms: The transmission slips or hesitates
the engine light comes on
the transmission drops into a lower gear
the vehicle stalls or loses power.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the shifter can cause the vehicle to become stuck in gear, leading to accidents or leaving the driver stranded.
symptoms: The shifter becomes stuck or difficult to shift
the vehicle is unable to shift into gear.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the rack and pinion steering system can cause loss of steering control, leading to accidents or leaving the driver stranded.
symptoms: Clunking or grinding sounds from the front wheels
loose or difficult steering
vibration while driving
sudden loss of steering control
tire wear on the inner or outer edges
and excessive play in the steering system.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the inner tie rod can cause loss of steering control, leading to accidents or leaving the driver stranded.
symptoms: Loose or difficult steering
vibration while driving
sudden loss of steering control
tire wear on the inner or outer edges
and excessive play in the steering system.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the steering control arm can cause loss of steering control, leading to accidents or leaving the driver stranded.
symptoms: Sudden loss of steering control
vibration while driving
and excessive play in the steering system.
